# ~/.memento/hints.md — local alias hints (NOT committed to the public repo)
#
# Injected into extraction prompts at runtime. Keep it short: entity aliases
# the extractor should treat as the same thing. Example format:

- "host-a" IS the headless inference host (runs Hermes Agent, llama.cpp, oMLX)
- "host-b" IS the primary desktop
- Models loaded by oMLX belong on the oMLX page unless the model itself is the topic
- Hermes config lives at ~/.hermes/config.yaml
